    "actor_description": "The energy comes up bright, like someone turned the lights on inside my ribs. Thoughts quicken and start connecting on their own-easy, playful, productive. I feel it in my hands and feet: the impulse to gesture, to move, to do something with this charge before it fades. My voice wants out of my throat. I'm not escaping anything; I'm leaning into it. Whatever's next, I want to meet it at speed and leave a mark.",
